doc\README.md:
   1: Cent Core
   6: [Cent Core](https://www.nortcrypto.com) is the original cent client and it builds the backbone of the network. However, it downloads and stores the entire history of cent transactions; depending on the speed of your computer and network connection, the synchronization process can take anywhere from a few hours to a day or more. Thankfully you only have to do this once.
