  16: - bin/32/cent-qt (GUI, 32-bit) or bin/32/centd (headless, 32-bit)
  17: - bin/64/cent-qt (GUI, 64-bit) or bin/64/centd (headless, 64-bit)
  21: Unpack the files into a directory, and then run cent-qt.exe.
  25: Drag cent-Qt to your applications folder, and then run cent-Qt.
  33: The following are developer notes on how to build cent on your native platform. They are not complete guides, but include notes on the necessary libraries, compile flags, etc.
